**Current Whisper Abilities**
• Bartender - Can whisper to the public tarvern channel at any time.
• Chef - Can whisper to their selected customer in the restaurant each day.
• Devil - Can whisper to the devil wager channel with the wager recipient each night.
• Flute Player - Can whisper to the enchanted channel at any time with all those who have been enchanted.
• Grandma - Can whisper with their selected player(s) each night.
• Corrupt Wolf - Can whisper with their selected player each night.

• *Cerberus - Can whisper with their offer of protection recipient each night.*
